<seg id=1> The international court in the Hague ruled that three defendants were guilty of committing war crimes against Bosnian Serbs, but found their commander not guilty. </seg>
<seg id=2> The international court judged that Bosnian Muslim Ferarice was not responsible for the atrocities committed against Serbian prisoners of war by his men in the Celebic Camp in 1992. </seg>
<seg id=3> The three accused have been sentenced to imprisonment because of their rule of terror in the POW camp. </seg>
